data.title: Donor Listing
data.text:
Seattle Rep is profoundly grateful for our donor family whose contributions at all levels throughout the years have made our work possible. Our supporters and the generosity of the individuals listed here are an important piece of the rich tapestry of artisans, volunteers, partners, patrons, staff, and more who all together put theater at the heart of public life.

The following list acknowledges individuals whose cumulative support of Seattle Rep between January 1, 2023 and April 14, 2024 totaled $30 or more, and is inclusive of gifts made towards general operations, the Endowment, Gala Raise the Paddle, capital investments, and matching gifts.

The accuracy of this list is important to us; we welcome notification of unintended omissions or errors. Please contact Donor Stewardship & Events Director Katelyn Woods with any questions.
